For Mode A (incorrect pre-vote promotion), remove the code that promotes pre-votes to grants in `_startElection`. Pre-votes are a gate to start an election, not a substitute for actual votes.

For Mode B (strict log comparison), change the `>` operator to `>=` in `_isLogUpToDate` to correctly implement the Raft log up-to-dateness rule.

